Text.string: How's the day treating ya, Vault Hunter?
I know who I was in my past life. Do you?
Do you know the difference between a bog, a swamp and a marsh? 'Cause no one else seems to!
The smell of that finely-aged Jakobs gunpowder is just divine.
The swamps of Eden make us strong! And gives us green lung... [cough]
You ever eaten a live grog? Follow up question, would ya like to?
If you wanna live free, you gotta be willing to fight for it... or to pay someone else to fight for it.
Just let me know if you need some backup out there!
We're gonna kick them sorry sons of bitches off Eden-6 one of these days!
I heard saurian tartare is considered a delicacy... but I'm just in it for the tail.
You ever listen to the grogs singing in the light of the moon? It's... horrible.
Do you know the swamp's secret? Well, if you find it out, you let me know, all right? All right.
The Crimson Raiders and Jakobs make a great team! Let's go kill some zealots!
I come from a long line of revolutionaries, rebels, freedom fighters... you get the picture.
I'm like a swamp. Deep. Mysterious. Full of mud. And I croak at night.
I don't know what the hell “Eden” means or where that word comes from. Maybe it's 'cause everything on Eden-6 wants to eat ya.
Does the air filtration recycle farts or what?
This ship smells. Oh wait, is that me?
I kinda miss the grog songs at night, horrible as they were. Am I homesick?
Dunno if I'll ever get used to the rumble of the Sanctuary engines.
Moxxi's bar is a good time. I recommend it!
And the Vault Hunter is OUT!
See ya, wouldn't want to be ya!
Don't you die on me! I mean... lata!
Don't come back without a bandit's head!
Kay, I'll join ya next fight!
I'm bored. Who wants to get into something?
Eden-6 is such a mess right now.
What makes someone turn bandit? I just don't understand it at all.
You'll know you've gone full crazy if them psychos start to make sense and you talk to yourself umprompted.
Let's go kill some zealots, y'all!
I am just so pumped to be here!
All right, all right, all right.
